sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , PROGRAM AS PROGRAMalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.CATEGORY = "MDE" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID AND PROGRAMalias0.NAME = "CS - LSA" AND PROGRAMalias0.PROGRAM_ID = PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.PROGRAM_ID AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "FA" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
